// interpolate json by replacing placeholders with variables
window.wc_ga_pro.interpolate_json = function( object, variables ) {

if ( ! variables ) {
return object;
}

var j = JSON.stringify( object );

for ( var k in variables ) {
j = j.split( '{$' + k + '}' ).join( variables[ k ] );
}

return JSON.parse( j );
};

// return the title for a payment gateway
window.wc_ga_pro.get_payment_method_title = function( payment_method ) {
return window.wc_ga_pro.available_gateways[ payment_method ] || payment_method;
};

// check if an email is valid
window.wc_ga_pro.is_valid_email = function( email ) {
return /[^\s@]+@[^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+/.test( email );
};

<script>

<!-- creating element a for images -->
document.querySelectorAll('.my_image_box').forEach(function (item) {
let elem = document.createElement('a');
elem.style.position = "absolute";
elem.style.top = "0";
elem.style.left = "0";
elem.style.paddingTop = item.querySelector('.image-cover').style.paddingTop;
elem.setAttribute('href', item.querySelector('.box-image a').getAttribute('href'));

item.append(elem);
})
<!-- End creating element a for images -->


<!-- improving testimonials -->
document.querySelectorAll('.my_testimonial').forEach(function (item) {
let name = item.querySelector('.testimonial-meta');
let rating = item.querySelector('.star-rating');
item.querySelector('.testimonial-meta').remove();
item.querySelector('.star-rating').remove();

let elem = document.createElement('div');
elem.classList.add("my_testimonial_inner");
elem.append(name);
elem.append(rating);

item.prepend(elem);
})
<!-- End improving testimonials -->


<!-- adding hover images for products -->
let bestSellingBundles = [
'https://nordace.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Siena-Pro-15-Traveler-Set.jpg',

document.querySelectorAll('.slider_products.slider').forEach(function (item) {

item.insertAdjacentHTML('afterbegin', `<div class="bg fill bg-fill bg-loaded" style="background-image: url(${bestSellingBundles[index]});"></div>`)
})
}
if (item.classList.contains('new_new_arrivals')) {

})

<!-- End adding hover images for products -->


<!-- arrow alignment relative to the image for slider-->
function changeTopArrow() {
document.querySelectorAll('.arrow_alignment.slider').forEach(function (item) {
let imgHeight = item.querySelector('img').clientHeight;
item.querySelectorAll('button.flickity-prev-next-button').forEach(function (item) {
item.style.top = imgHeight/2 + "px";
})
})
}

window.addEventListener('resize', changeTopArrow);
<!-- End arrow alignment relative to the image for slider-->


<!-- changing slider height -->
function changeHeightSlider() {
document.querySelectorAll('.LP_Slider.change_height').forEach(function (item) {
let slider = item.querySelectorAll('.row:not(.not_slider)>.col>.col-inner');
slider.forEach(function (item) {
item.style.minHeight = 0 + "px";
})

let maxHeightSlide = Array.from(slider).reduce(function (previusValue, currentValue) {
return Math.max(previusValue, currentValue.clientHeight);
}, 0);

slider.forEach(function (item) {
item.style.minHeight = maxHeightSlide + "px";
})
})
}

window.addEventListener('resize', changeHeightSlider);
<!-- end changing slider height -->



<!-- adding classes for my_tabs -->
document.querySelectorAll('.my_tabs2 .nav-pills .tab a').forEach(function (item) {
item.classList.add("button");
item.classList.add("white");
item.classList.add("is-larger");
item.classList.add("lowercase");
})
<!-- End adding classes for my_tabs -->


<!-- setting the width for tabs -->
function setWidthTabs() {
document.querySelectorAll('.my_tabs2>ul').forEach(function (item) {
if (window.innerWidth > 549) {
item.style.height = "unset";
item.querySelectorAll('li').forEach(function (item) {
item.style.left = "unset";
})
} else {
item.style.height = item.querySelector('li').clientHeight + "px";
let width = 20;

item.querySelectorAll('li').forEach(function (item) {
item.style.left = width + "px";
width += item.clientWidth;
})
}
});
}

window.addEventListener('resize', setWidthTabs);
<!-- end setting the width for tabs -->


<!-- instagram video -->
const videos = document.querySelectorAll(".instagram video");

videos.forEach(video => {
video.closest(".inst").addEventListener("pointerover", function () {
this.querySelector("video").play()
})
video.closest(".inst").addEventListener("pointerout", function () {
this.querySelector("video").pause()
})
video.closest(".inst").addEventListener("touchstart", function () {
this.querySelector("video").play()
})
video.closest(".inst").addEventListener("touchend", function () {
this.querySelector("video").pause()
})
})
<!-- end instagram video -->


jQuery(document).ready(function ($) {

let block_show_1 = false;
let block_show_2 = false;
function is_shown(target, block_show) {
if (block_show) {
return false;
}

var wt = $(window).scrollTop();
var wh = $(window).height();
var et = $(target).offset().top;
var eh = $(target).outerHeight();
var dh = $(document).height();
if (wt + wh >= et || wh + wt == dh || eh + et < wh) {
block_show = true;
return true;
} else {
return false;
}
}

$(window).scroll(function(){ if(is_shown($('.best_selling_bundles.slider', block_show_1))) {
changeTopArrow();
} });
$(document).ready(function(){ if(is_shown($('.best_selling_bundles.slider', block_show_1))) {
changeTopArrow();
} });

$(window).scroll(function(){ if(is_shown($('.LP_Slider.Reviews', block_show_2))) {
changeHeightSlider();
} });
$(document).ready(function(){ if(is_shown($('.LP_Slider.Reviews', block_show_2))) {
changeHeightSlider();
} });

})


</script>



<script>
// Function to determine the language from the URL
function getLanguageFromUrl() {
const languageMatch = window.location.pathname.match(/\/(en|ja|tw|de|es|it|fr)\//);
return languageMatch ? languageMatch[1] : 'en'; // Default to English if not matched
}

// Function to get the appropriate discount text based on language
function getDiscountText(discountPercentage, language) {
switch (language) {
case 'de':
return discountPercentage + "% RABATT";
case 'es':
return discountPercentage + "% DE DTO.";
case 'it':
return "-" + discountPercentage + "%";
case 'fr':
return "-" + discountPercentage + "%";
case 'en':
case 'ja':
case 'tw':
default:
return discountPercentage + "% OFF";
}
}

// Function to check if the current page is a VIP page
function isVipPage() {
return window.location.href.includes("vip");
}

function extractPrice(priceText) {
// Use a regular expression to extract the numeric value from the price text
const priceMatch = priceText.match(/(\d+[\d,\.]*)/);
if (priceMatch) {
return parseFloat(priceMatch[0].replace(/,/g, ''));
}
return null;
}
function formatPrice(price, maxDecimalPlaces) {
// Format the number with fixed decimal places and commas for thousands
return price.toFixed(maxDecimalPlaces).replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, ",");
}
function getDecimalPlaces(value) {
if (Math.floor(value) !== value) {
return value.toString().split(".")[1].length || 0;
}
return 0;
}

let maxDecimalPlaces = 0;

// Get all the products within the container
const products = document.querySelectorAll(".row.products_style .col");

products.forEach(product => {

const originalPriceElement = product.querySelector("del span.woocommerce-Price-amount bdi");
const discountedPriceElement = product.querySelector("ins span.woocommerce-Price-amount bdi");

if (!originalPriceElement || !discountedPriceElement) return;

const originalPrice = extractPrice(originalPriceElement.textContent);
const discountedPrice = extractPrice(discountedPriceElement.textContent);
const originalPriceDecimals = getDecimalPlaces(originalPrice);
const discountedPriceDecimals = getDecimalPlaces(discountedPrice);

maxDecimalPlaces = Math.max(maxDecimalPlaces, originalPriceDecimals, discountedPriceDecimals);

if (originalPrice === null || discountedPrice === null) return;

const rawDiscountPercentage = ((originalPrice - discountedPrice) / originalPrice) * 100;
let discountPercentage = rawDiscountPercentage < 1 ? rawDiscountPercentage.toFixed(1) : Math.round(rawDiscountPercentage);

let isExtraDiscountElement = product.closest('[class*="extra_"]');
if (isExtraDiscountElement) {
let extraDiscount = +isExtraDiscountElement.className.match(/(?<=\bextra_)\d+/);
let newDiscountedPrice = (discountedPrice * ( 100 - extraDiscount ) / 100).toFixed(2);
discountPercentage = Math.round(100 - (newDiscountedPrice * 100 / originalPrice));
discountedPriceElement.textContent = discountedPriceElement.textContent.replace(/(\d+[\d,\.]*)/, newDiscountedPrice )
};
const language = getLanguageFromUrl();
const discountText = getDiscountText(discountPercentage, language);

const badgeContainer = product.querySelector(".badge-container");
const discountBadge = document.createElement("div");
discountBadge.textContent = discountText;
discountBadge.style.background = "#971b1b";
discountBadge.style.color = "white";
discountBadge.style.paddingLeft = "10px";
discountBadge.style.paddingRight = "10px";
badgeContainer.innerHTML = ""; // Clear existing badges
badgeContainer.appendChild(discountBadge);
});

const bfExclusive40Products = document.querySelectorAll(".bf_exclusive_40 .col");

bfExclusive40Products.forEach(product => {
const originalPriceElement = product.querySelector("del span.woocommerce-Price-amount bdi");
const existingSalePriceElement = product.querySelector("ins span.woocommerce-Price-amount bdi");

const priceElement = existingSalePriceElement || product.querySelector("span.woocommerce-Price-amount bdi");
if (!priceElement) return;

// Extract the currency symbol
const currencySymbolMatch = priceElement.textContent.match(/[^\d\s,\.]+/);
const currencySymbol = currencySymbolMatch ? currencySymbolMatch[0] : "$"; // Default to "$" if not found

let basePrice = originalPriceElement ? extractPrice(originalPriceElement.textContent) : extractPrice(priceElement.textContent);
const existingSalePrice = existingSalePriceElement ? extractPrice(existingSalePriceElement.textContent) : null;

if (basePrice === null) return;

// Determine the regular and sale prices
const regularPrice = existingSalePriceElement ? existingSalePrice : basePrice;
const newSalePrice = regularPrice * 0.6;

const priceWrapper = product.querySelector(".price-wrapper");
priceWrapper.innerHTML = ""; // Clear existing content

// Display the regular price crossed out
const crossedOutPrice = document.createElement("del");
crossedOutPrice.innerHTML = `<span class="woocommerce-Price-amount amount"><bdi>${currencySymbol}&nbsp;${formatPrice(regularPrice, maxDecimalPlaces)}</bdi></span>`;
priceWrapper.appendChild(crossedOutPrice);

// Display the new sale price
const newPrice = document.createElement("ins");
newPrice.innerHTML = `<span class="woocommerce-Price-amount amount"><bdi>${currencySymbol}&nbsp;${formatPrice(newSalePrice, maxDecimalPlaces)}</bdi></span>`;
priceWrapper.appendChild(newPrice);
const language = getLanguageFromUrl();
const discountText = getDiscountText(40, language);

jQuery(document).ready(function ($) {
function getUrlParam(name) {
name = name.replace(/[\[]/, '\\[').replace(/[\]]/, '\\]');
var regex = new RegExp('[\\?&]' + name + '=([^&#]*)');
var results = regex.exec(location.search);
return results === null ? '' : decodeURIComponent(results[1].replace(/\+/g, ' '));
}
// Check if the 'go' URL parameter is set and not empty
var affiliateUsernameParam = getUrlParam('go');
var utmSourceParam = getUrlParam('utm_source');
if (affiliateUsernameParam || utmSourceParam == 'influencer_ir' || utmSourceParam == 'influencer_sc') {
// Set the cookie to prevent the newsletter popup
cookie('lightbox_newsletter-signup-link', 'opened_1', { expires: 3 });
}
var autoApply = false;
if (autoApply) {
$('#redeem-text').hide();
$('#redeem-btn').hide();
$('#coupon-box').hide(); // Hide if automatically applying
}
});
